  "result": "## Phase 1: Project Initialization & Database Design — Complete ✅\n\nAll 6 target files were found pre-existing and verified. Here's a breakdown of what's in place:\n\n---\n\n### 📦 Root `package.json`\nMonorepo with npm workspaces configured for `backend/` and `frontend/`. Includes scripts for `start`, `test`, `db:init`, and `db:test`.\n\n---\n\n### 🗄️ Backend (`backend/`)\n\n| File | What it does |\n|---|---|\n| `package.json` | Declares `pg` and `dotenv` as runtime dependencies |\n| `.env` | Template with `DB_HOST`, `DB_PORT`, `DB_NAME`, `DB_USER`, `DB_PASSWORD` — **never commit this** |\n| `config/db.js` | Pool with 20 max connections, idle timeout, `healthCheck()`, and `runSchema()` helper |\n| `schema.sql` | Full schema: `users` → `profiles` → `tasks` → `subtasks`, with FK constraints, indexes, and `updated_at` triggers |\n| `tests/db.test.js` | 4 integration tests (connection, query, client acquire/release, pool health) — **skips gracefully** when DB credentials are absent |\n\n**Schema highlights:**\n- `users` — core auth identity (username, email, password_hash)\n- `profiles` — extended info with JSONB `preferences` field\n- `tasks` — tracks code generation jobs with DAG `plan_tree` + `result_json` in JSONB\n- `subtasks` — individual DAG nodes with `dependencies` JSONB array and per-row status\n- Auto-`updated_at` triggers on all tables; composite unique constraint on `(task_id, subtask_id)`\n\n---\n\n### 🌐 Frontend (`frontend/index.html`)\nClean single-page UI with system font stack, centered layout, and a Phase 1 status badge.\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ One prerequisite before running tests\n\n```bash\nnpm install          # install pg + dotenv into workspaces\nnpm run db:init      # apply schema.sql against your PostgreSQL instance\nnpm run db:test      # run the integration test suite\n```\n\nSet real credentials in `backend/.env` (copy from the template) before `db:init`.",
